---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Home">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-yellow-500 text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Kailash Research Foundation (KRF)</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8">Where Research Meets Human Resolve</p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          KRF exists to bridge the gap between the complex challenges communities face and the solutions they deserve, 
          combining a scientific approach with lived understanding to design systems that are inclusive, resilient, and built to last.
        </p>
        <a href="#involved" class="inline-block bg-white text-yellow-500 font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-yellow-100 transition-colors">
          Get Involved
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Values Section -->
  <section id="values" class="py-16 bg-yellow-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Core Values</h2>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center bg-white border-2 border-yellow-400 rounded-full px-6 py-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-yellow-600">Inclusivity</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-center">Every voice matters</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center bg-white border-2 border-yellow-400 rounded-full px-6 py-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-yellow-600">Representation</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-center">Diverse communities at the table</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center bg-white border-2 border-yellow-400 rounded-full px-6 py-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-yellow-600">Equity</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-center">Fair opportunities for all</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center bg-white border-2 border-yellow-400 rounded-full px-6 py-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-yellow-600">Public-Centric</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-center">People's needs first</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center bg-white border-2 border-yellow-400 rounded-full px-6 py-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-yellow-600">Understanding Heterogeneity</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-center">Embracing diversity</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center bg-white border-2 border-yellow-400 rounded-full px-6 py-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-yellow-600">Growth & Adaptability</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-center">Evolving with change</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center bg-white border-2 border-yellow-400 rounded-full px-6 py-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-yellow-600">Wisdom & Fearlessness</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-center">Courage with knowledge</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section id="about" class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Our Story</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="mb-4">
            Kailash Research Foundation (KRF) was born out of a legacy quietly built, not declared. My grandparents believed that the most profound impact is made not through words, but through the way one lives. Their lives were defined by acts of generosity and integrity that asked for no recognition, yet left deep, lasting imprints on the people around them. KRF is my way of carrying forward that tradition, grounded in altruism, sustained by action.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            On the field, these challenges never stand alone — they are intertwined with caste, religion, and social inequities, creating complex realities that demand solutions built on a scientific approach and a deep understanding of people's lived realities.
          </p>
          <p>
            KRF rests on a simple belief: change is not enough — evolution is the goal. change makes things work a little better; evolution reshapes them so they no longer carry the same flaws. Our work is to design systems that are inclusive, resilient, and built to endure — systems that not only resolve today's challenges but open the way for communities to thrive on their own in the future.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Areas of Focus Section -->
  <section id="focus" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Areas of Focus</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-600">Policy Research & Recommendations</h3>
          <p>Conducting evidence-based research to shape policies that address complex, interconnected social issues, with solutions that work in both national and when needed, global contexts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-600">Human Rights</h3>
          <p>Advancing equity by focusing on the upliftment of communities facing systemic barriers, ensuring freedom from discrimination and building pathways to dignity for all.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-600">Women</h3>
          <p>Driving both grassroots initiatives and policy measures that strengthen women's rights, amplify their voices, and expand their representation in decision-making spaces.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-600">Health Access</h3>
          <p>Improving primary and localised healthcare systems to deliver consistent, high-quality services, ensuring that essential care is accessible to every community.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-600">Practical Education</h3>
          <p>Filling the gap left by traditional schooling by equipping all age groups with essential real-world knowledge, from financial literacy to legal awareness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Roadmap & Plans Section -->
  <section id="roadmap" class="py-16 bg-yellow-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Roadmap & Plans</h2>

      <!-- Timeline Container -->
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative">

        <!-- Timeline Line -->
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-yellow-300 transform -translate-x-1/2"></div>

        <!-- Next 12 Months Section -->
        <div class="mb-16 relative">
          <div class="md:flex items-center mb-8">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 pr-8 md:text-right mb-4 md:mb-0">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-600">Next 12 Months</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Building strong foundations</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center items-center">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-yellow-500 border-4 border-white shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
                1
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
              <p class="text-gray-800">
                In its first year, KRF will focus on building strong roots while taking decisive early steps.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 12 Month Milestones -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-yellow-500 transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                  <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">1</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Community Outreach</h4>
              </div>
              <p>Conduct outreach in selected districts to understand local realities firsthand.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
            <div class="hidden md:block"></div>

            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-yellow-500 transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                  <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">2</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Women's Safety</h4>
              </div>
              <p>Design practical, community-driven solutions to improve women's safety.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-yellow-500 transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                  <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">3</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Education Initiatives</h4>
              </div>
              <p>Host gatherings for children and youth aimed at bridging critical education gaps.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
            <div class="hidden md:block"></div>

            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-yellow-500 transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                  <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold">4</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Network Building</h4>
              </div>
              <p>Form networks with relevant government channels and civic bodies to accelerate impact.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3-5 Year Vision Section -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="md:flex items-center mb-8">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 pr-8 md:text-right mb-4 md:mb-0">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-600">3–5 Year Vision</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Expanding our impact</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center items-center">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-yellow-500 border-4 border-white shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
                2
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
              <p class="text-gray-800">
                Our goal is to establish KRF as a respected think tank with the capacity to deliver on-ground reforms.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Long-term Vision Cards -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-yellow-500 transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-yellow-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Research Excellence</h4>
              </div>
              <p>Developing high-quality research and policy recommendations that address complex social issues.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-yellow-500 transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-yellow-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Community Engagement</h4>
              </div>
              <p>Combining rigorous analysis with active community engagement, ensuring our work is both deeply informed and immediately relevant.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-yellow-500 transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-yellow-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Institutional Partnerships</h4>
              </div>
              <p>Directly implementing solutions in partnership with communities, institutions, and government bodies.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-md border-l-4 border-yellow-500 transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-yellow-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Sustainable Impact</h4>
              </div>
              <p>Ensuring our ideas don't just live on paper — they live in people's lives and create lasting positive change.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder's Message Section -->
  <section id="founders" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Founder's Message</h2>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <p class="text-lg italic text-center mb-8">
          "At KRF, we believe that transformation is strongest when it is grounded in both insight and action. Our mission is to bridge the gap between the realities communities face and the solutions they deserve, creating systems that are as resilient as they are inclusive."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-600">Raveena Palli, Co-Founder</h3>
          <p>
            Worked across 250+ districts in India, she has led initiatives in policy research, electoral strategy, and grassroots development. Her work spans designing evidence-based solutions in health access, education, women's empowerment, and human rights, currently serving as an election advisor— always recognising that these challenges are deeply interconnected. She brings the perspective of someone who has worked in both the halls of policy and on the ground with communities, ensuring that every solution we design is practical, inclusive, and built to last.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-600">Lakshya N. Palli, Co-Founder</h3>
          <p>
            An IIT graduate and accomplished RTL designer with expertise in design synthesis, modem, and Wi-Fi technologies. A star scholar and sports enthusiast, Lakshya is driven by building businesses that thrive in partnership with the communities they serve.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-lg">
          KRF is our shared platform to unite research, policy, and community action. We see it as a space where ideas evolve into tangible, lasting transformation. If our vision resonates with you, we welcome you to connect, collaborate, and grow alongside us.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Get Involved Section -->
  <section id="involved" class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Get Involved</h2>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">
          KRF is in its first chapter and this is when every voice, skill, and idea matters the most. While our formal projects are in development, there are already ways for individuals, institutions, and communities to connect with us:
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-600">Collaborate on Research</h3>
            <p>Partner with us on studies, field surveys, and policy recommendations.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-600">Volunteer Your Skills</h3>
            <p>From field outreach to design, data analysis to community facilitation — your expertise can help shape impactful work.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-600">Host Conversations</h3>
            <p>Co-create dialogues, workshops, and knowledge-sharing sessions with us.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-yellow-600">Stay Updated</h3>
            <p>Join our mailing list to hear about upcoming projects, events, and opportunities to contribute.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg text-center">
          Whether you are an individual with a vision, an organisation with aligned goals, or a community group with on-the-ground insights, we want to hear from you.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <a href="mailto:info@krf.org" class="inline-block bg-yellow-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-yellow-600 transition-colors">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
